( forget the part about Ra praying and stuff. Ive had alot of work to do so i 
really wasnt thinking about it at the time. )

::: Ra waled closely behinde Set. He was much bigger than set, broader and 
stronger. He wore and Egyptian Headset that flowed down his shoulders and was 
topped of with a hissing Cobra. :::

:: Set :: Alright, theyre in there. I want you to watch them carefully while 
Im gone getting this...transmetal 2 tech box. Its important.

::: Ra slammed his right Pheniox talon agianst his chest and bowed. His huge 
red wings were folded behinde his back like red armor. ::: 

::: Ra ::: Yes Master Set. I will do as you ask.

::: Set then stared into his bright orange eyes, and left Ra as he entered 
the holding chamber. :::

~~~~~~~~~~~~

::: Megatron, in his blank proto-form, watched the large bot walk across the 
room and sit at a control station. :::

::: Hell Beast, from across the hall ::: Who are you? Did Set bring a small 
army with him?

::: Ra said with a brisk, sharp voice ::: I am his army!

::: With the flick of a few buttons, a red force feild lit up and Hell Beast, 
Megatron, and Jackle fell to the ground in severe pain. :::

::: Ra ::: There will be no talking, not on my watch.

~~~~~~~~~~

::: Set transformed into his Puma beastmode and headed for the Predacon base, 
to get the techbox. :::
